cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.RO, cs.MM

This paper is about deep learning approaches to optical flow estimation, which is a computer vision task. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also proposes a new iterative residual refinement scheme based on weight sharing, which is related to machine learning and optimization, making cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) likely categories as well. The paper also mentions occlusion prediction, which is related to robotics and autonomous systems, making cs.RO (Robotics) a possible category. Finally, the paper deals with image processing and analysis, which is related to multimedia, making cs.MM (Multimedia) a possible category as well.
